event.title: Artificial Intelligence Training Free Demo
event.description:
Intellipaat is organising a free demo for AI learners online. The demo is for the AI Training in Bangalore to help master CNN, Tensorflow, graph visualization, RNN, Deep learning libraries, back propagation and much more.

What will you learn in this Artificial Intelligence Course?

  1. Deep learning Basics
  2. Understand ANN (Artificial Neural Network)
  3. Learning Tensorflow
  4. ML using Python

Who should take up this course?

Professionals working in Data Science, analytics, e-commerce, search engine, etc.
